3174,"uid":86949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da77dad7e00d18bc3ca9707b312fbd33b6c1ea79","tid":1363174,"uid":85836,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"繼續推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7LqTpo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7LqTpo.png&h=3670bc9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4dfadc95f44d71ccc0504d49644360d6fcd971d","tid":1363174,"uid":85836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8143b6fcdc106520dda2b4a24b48575c9cabc83d","tid":1363174,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"多謝車長！"},{"pid":"cc66e6876c00e052398f91de27a99b20cce83023","tid":1363174,"uid":267189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺Google Form/ Telegram/ facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook